# Force LF line endings for all text files regardless of checkout platform.
# Rationale: setup.sh was tripped by CRLF-ized .tool-versions on Windows
# (core.autocrlf=true default injects \r into parsed shell values). Rather
# than maintain per-extension exceptions, normalize everything to LF.
#
# On first clone (or after renormalize), the working tree matches the repo
# byte-for-byte on any OS.
*   text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary declarations so git doesn't try to diff them as text.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
